Well, excuse me for not having a supercomputer.

1039
01:05:25,000 --> 01:05:25,800
你好?
Hello?

1040
01:05:28,000 --> 01:05:30,000
好 德裡克
Oh. Hey, Derek.

1041
01:05:30,400 --> 01:05:32,900
怎麼樣? 維吉爾 要幫我嗎? 夥計
What do you say, Virg? Gonna help me out, buddy?

1042
01:05:37,200 --> 01:05:38,400
當然...
Yeah, sure...

1043
01:05:39,700 --> 01:05:40,600
...D石頭
...D-rock.

1044
01:05:52,600 --> 01:05:54,600
早 喜鵲!
Ahh!         Good morning, Magpie!

1045
01:05:54,700 --> 01:05:57,400
你媽媽讓我進來的 今天真是不錯的一天
Your mom let me in. lt is such a nice day l was thinking

1046
01:05:57,700 --> 01:06:00,200
也許 可以出去走走 談談我們的未來
we could go on a walk and talk about our future.

1047
01:06:00,300 --> 01:06:01,700
然後...
And then... oh!

1048
01:06:02,800 --> 01:06:04,200
我想要個橙子屋      結果!
l'd like an orange house.         The results!

1049
01:06:04,900 --> 01:06:07,400
你不需要地址 在信封上只用寫
You wouldn't need an address. On the envelope you just say

1050
01:06:07,600 --> 01:06:09,700
"珍妮特·帕切拉斯科,橙子屋"
''Jeanette Pachelewski, orange house.''

1051
01:06:11,200 --> 01:06:12,000
完成了!
lt's done!

1052
01:06:16,400 --> 01:06:18,700
我不是個科學家
Oh, um, l'm no scientist,

1053
01:06:18,800 --> 01:06:20,300
但看上去情況不太妙
but that doesn't look good.

1054
01:06:21,800 --> 01:06:23,100
我們製造出了一個...一個...
We created a... a...

1055
01:06:23,900 --> 01:06:26,800
一個...一個...快說呀 藍鳥
A... a... Spit it out, Bluebird.

1056
01:06:27,800 --> 01:06:28,900
一個黑洞
A black hole.

1057
01:06:30,900 --> 01:06:31,900
很糟糕 是不是?
That's bad, right?

1058
01:06:32,900 --> 01:06:34,600
隨著時間的流失
As the timeline continues,

1059
01:06:34,700 --> 01:06:37,300
我們可以看到
we see an increased number of occurrences

1060
01:06:37,417 --> 01:06:39,299
在薩莫頓區域事件的擴大
here in the Summerton area.

1061
01:06:39,300 --> 01:06:42,600
如果我們都翻到47頁 能看到加亮區...
lf we can all turn to page 47, we can see where l highlighted...

1062
01:06:42,700 --> 01:06:43,800
我撒謊了...
Hey!        l lied!

1063
01:06:44,900 --> 01:06:46,628
我偷了方程式
l stole the formula

1064
01:06:46,768 --> 01:06:48,299
我們進行了時間穿梭
we've been time-traveling all over the place.

1065
01:06:48,300 --> 01:06:51,000
先你一步 向你介紹太平洋技術中心地震部
Way ahead of you. l'd like you to meet Doctors Connors

1066
01:06:51,100 --> 01:06:54,300
康納斯博士和溫多普博士
and Winthorpe from the seismology department at Pacific Tech.

1067
01:06:54,600 --> 01:06:57,300
博士 這是查理·塔特爾
Doctors, this is Charles Tuttle.

1068
01:06:57,700 --> 01:07:00,500
你是誰? 9歲男孩      他14歲
What are you, nine years old?         He's fourteen.

1069
01:07:00,800 --> 01:07:03,400
好些了 現在不覺得是個失敗者了
That's better. Now l don't feel like such a loser.

1070
01:07:03,500 --> 01:07:04,800
那你們已經知道黑洞的事了?
So you already know about the black hole?

1071
01:07:07,100 --> 01:07:08,800
什麼?      黑洞!
What?        The black hole!

1072
01:07:09,700 --> 01:07:11,500
我知道你們資金不足 但別這樣
l knew you guys were underfunded, but come on.

1073
01:07:11,600 --> 01:07:14,400
真可笑 我們想過各種最壞的結果
Preposterous. We ran the worst case scenario several times.

1074
01:07:14,500 --> 01:07:16,500
從沒想到過黑洞
We never came up with a black hole.

1075
01:07:16,600 --> 01:07:20,000
我發現有五六個小數沒有繼續
l see five, six decimals that weren't carried over.

1076
01:07:20,700 --> 01:07:22,400
噢
Hmm.

1077
01:07:24,400 --> 01:07:26,800
是啊 "噢"
Oops.        Yeah, oops.

1078
01:07:28,300 --> 01:07:29,483
每次我們用那個機器
Each time we used the machine

1079
01:07:29,637 --> 01:07:31,499
空間時間連續性上的裂縫
the rift in the space-time continuum

1080
01:07:31,500 --> 01:07:34,900
就沒有消失 現在這些波動合在了一起
did not disappear. lnstead the fluctuations blended together

1081
01:07:35,000 --> 01:07:37,300
形成了一個巨大的黑洞
to create one giant black hole.

1082
01:07:37,700 --> 01:07:38,778
黑洞最嚴重的地區會擴展開
The worst part is the black hole

1083
01:07:38,949 --> 01:07:41,599
直到吞掉"薩莫頓"
will spread until it swallows up Summerton.

1084
01:07:41,600 --> 01:07:44,100
然後就是整個西北 接著是整個美國
Then the Northwest, then the entire United States.

1085
01:07:47,200 --> 01:07:48,000
以此類推
And so on.

1086
01:07:48,200 --> 01:07:49,607
還剩多久?
How much time till zero hour?

1087
01:07:49,750 --> 01:07:51,859
據我估計...
According to my estimates we have...

1088
01:07:53,400 --> 01:07:55,600
...離世界毀滅還剩不到4小時
...less than four hours till the end of the world.

1089
01:07:55,800 --> 01:07:57,116
夥計們 我們要拉響紅色警報
OK, people, we are going to Code Red.

1090
01:07:57,274 --> 01:07:58,999
接通華盛頓 馬上
Get Washington on the phone, now!

1091
01:07:59,000 --> 01:08:01,700
有一個方法可以扭轉局勢 不過是個遠射
There might be a way to reverse it, but it's a longshot.

1092
01:08:02,300 --> 01:08:04,400
說來聽聽吧 長官
Well, let's hear it, sir.

1093
01:08:18,000 --> 01:08:20,500
今晚的舞會讓我激動 維吉爾
l'm excited for the dance tonight.

1094
01:08:21,000 --> 01:08:21,900
你知道嗎?
And you know what?

1095
01:08:23,200 --> 01:08:24,800
我真高興你能跟我來
l'm really glad you're coming with me.

1096
01:08:26,200 --> 01:08:28,700
要不朋友是幹什麼的?      少來
Hey, what are friends for?         Come on.

1097
01:09:02,700 --> 01:09:04,700
一切就緒?      是的
Everything set?        Uh, yeah.

1098
01:09:04,800 --> 01:09:07,012
衣服在棒球場
The suits are in the basement

1099
01:09:07,191 --> 01:09:09,099
我們穿過咖啡廳下的隧道過去
we'll go through the tunnels under the cafeteria.

1100
01:09:09,100 --> 01:09:11,400
挺好 他們一宣佈贏家我們就走
Sweet. We'll go as soon as they announce the winners.

1101
01:09:14,900 --> 01:09:15,700
好啊 維吉爾
Hey, Virgil.

1102
01:09:23,800 --> 01:09:24,800
斯蒂芬...
Steph...

1103
01:09:26,400 --> 01:09:28,147
你相信人的一生
Do you believe that a person's life

1104
01:09:28,306 --> 01:09:30,999
在一瞬間就能改變嗎?
can change in a single moment?

1105
01:09:31,000 --> 01:09:34,600
有時是變好 有時只會更爛?
Sometimes for the better, other times for the worse?

1106
01:09:35,200 --> 01:09:36,700
我想是的
Yeah, l guess.

1107
01:09:37,800 --> 01:09:41,300
我們生命中的一刻即將被改寫
There's a moment in one of our lives that's about to change.

1108
01:09:41,500 --> 01:09:44,600
不知道是會變好還是變壞
And l don't know if it's for the better or for the worse.

1109
01:09:45,300 --> 01:09:48,100
維吉爾 我不大明白
Virgil, um, l'm not following.

1110
01:09:55,500 --> 01:09:56,700
注意...
Uh, attention...

1111
01:10:02,100 --> 01:10:04,600
大家都注意了
Um, attention everyone.

1112
01:10:04,700 --> 01:10:08,600
該是宣佈舞會國王和王后的時候了
lt's time to announce this year's king and queen of the dance.

1113
01:10:08,900 --> 01:10:10,200
但先來段...
But first...

1114
01:10:11,500 --> 01:10:13,900
寶貝 雷德 我想熱一點
Sonny, Red, and l wanna fry up some

1115
01:10:14,000 --> 01:10:15,518
花生黃油和香蕉三明治
peanut butter and banana sandwiches.

1116
01:10:15,686 --> 01:10:23,799
謝謝 非常感謝
Thank you. Thank you very much.

1117
01:10:23,800 --> 01:10:26,000
這是貓王艾維斯·普裡斯萊 有人知道嗎?
lt's Elvis Presley. Anyone?

1118
01:10:26,700 --> 01:10:28,900
不會吧 是個很有天賦的...隨便吧
Come on, that was a brilliant... Whatever.

1119
01:10:30,800 --> 01:10:32,100
斯蒂芬妮·詹姆森還有維吉爾·福克斯
Stephanie Jameson and Virgil Fox

1120
01:10:32,200 --> 01:10:33,000
上來吧 你們贏了
get up here. You won.

1121
01:10:36,000 --> 01:10:39,300
真讓人吃驚      哪有
This is such a surprise.          Not really.

1122
01:10:39,500 --> 01:10:40,432
為了保證我們能贏
To guarantee we'd win

1123
01:10:40,588 --> 01:10:42,399
我準時趕回來 塞滿了投票箱
l went back in time and stuffed the ballot box.

1124
01:10:42,400 --> 01:10:43,400
什麼?
What?

1125
01:10:49,200 --> 01:10:52,400
詹姆森小姐和福克斯先生
Miss Jameson and Mr. Fox.

1126
01:10:52,500 --> 01:10:54,600
別讓它離開你腦袋 還有時間查票
Don't let it go to your head. There's still time for a recount.

1127
01:11:14,200 --> 01:11:17,400
你真的塞滿了那個盒子?
So, um, did you really stuff the box?

1128
01:11:18,300 --> 01:11:19,300
是的
Yeah.

1129
01:11:19,900 --> 01:11:23,200
你 當然 不然誰會投我票?
l mean, you, sure, but who would vote for me?

1130
01:11:26,100 --> 01:11:27,300
我會
l would.

1131
01:11:32,300 --> 01:11:35,400
這太奇怪了      是啊
This is weird.         Yeah.

1132
01:11:37,700 --> 01:11:40,000
為什麼?      一個不錯的奇怪
Why?        A good weird.

1133
01:11:41,500 --> 01:11:43,800
確實      你怎麼能跟某人做這麼長
Right.         How you can be friends with someone

1134
01:11:44,100 --> 01:11:45,700
時間的朋友...
for so long, then...

1135
01:11:46,800 --> 01:11:50,600
這不一樣      一個不錯的不一樣
lt's different..          A good different.

1136
01:11:54,300 --> 01:11:57,400
來吧 兄弟 該走了      噢 關於那個
Come on, brother, it's time to go.           Oh, about that.

1137
01:11:57,500 --> 01:11:59,800
我想 我反悔了      你答應過的
l think l changed my mind.         You promised.

1138
01:12:00,200 --> 01:12:02,700
維吉爾?      哪也別去 我待會就回來
Virgil?        Don't go anywhere. l'll be right back.

1139
01:12:05,800 --> 01:12:08,800
我知道維吉爾搶走斯蒂芬妮會讓德雷克抓狂
l knew Derek would be hacked about Virgil bringing Stephanie.

1140
01:12:09,100 --> 01:12:10,200
打!
Fight!

1141
01:12:11,000 --> 01:12:13,700
不      打 打
Oh, no.         Fight, fight.

1142
01:12:16,100 --> 01:12:18,400
德裡克 等等 我們能談談嗎?
Derek, wait up. Can we talk about this?

1143
01:12:20,500 --> 01:12:21,800
哦 天哪
Oh, man.

1144
01:12:27,100 --> 01:12:29,700
斯蒂芬妮 維吉爾去哪兒了?
Stephanie, where's Virgil?

1145
01:12:29,800 --> 01:12:31,600
他和德裡克出去了      為什麼?
He left with Derek.         Why?

1146
01:12:32,400 --> 01:12:34,100
別告訴我他又要跳回到過去?
Don't tell me he's going to jump back in time?

1147
01:12:36,200 --> 01:12:37,600
上帝 他就是要這麼做!
Oh my gosh, that's what he's doing!

1148
01:12:37,900 --> 01:12:39,400
他會把事情搞的一團糟的!
He might make things worse!

1149
01:12:40,400 --> 01:12:43,900
借過! 對不起!      比世界末日還要糟糕?
Excuse me! Sorry!         Worse than the end of the world?

1150
01:12:48,800 --> 01:12:51,000
德裡克 我不能這麼做
Derek, l don't think l can do this.

1151
01:12:52,600 --> 01:12:53,700
什麼? 為什麼?
What, why?

1152
01:12:54,800 --> 01:12:57,400
斯蒂芬妮 我只是...只是覺得...
Stephanie. l just... l just think...

1153
01:12:58,100 --> 01:13:00,600
夥計 別告訴我 你想要搶我的女人
Dude, don't tell me you're going to try to steal my girl.

1154
01:13:04,000 --> 01:13:07,000
你是我的朋友 朋友之間不能那麼做
We're friends. l mean, buddies don't do that to each other.

1155
01:13:07,100 --> 01:13:08,800
維吉爾! 維吉爾·福克斯!
Virgil! Virgil Fox!

1156
01:13:09,800 --> 01:13:11,300
維吉爾 我們有點小麻煩
Virgil, we have a small problem.

1157
01:13:12,000 --> 01:13:15,600
只剩不到一個小時來拯救整個星球!
We have less than an hour to save the planet!

1158
01:13:15,700 --> 01:13:16,518
你在說什麼?
What are you talking about?

1159
01:13:16,657 --> 01:13:19,399
好吧 好吧 這裡怎麼了?
Well, well. What do we have here, hmm?

1160
01:13:19,400 --> 01:13:21,400
看來要開始一場騷亂
Looks like the beginnings of a fracas.

1161
01:13:21,600 --> 01:13:23,300
一場什麼?      一場騷亂!
A what?        A fracas!

1162
01:13:23,400 --> 01:13:26,100
戰爭      晚上留校
lt's a fight.         We'll sort out the detentions later.

1163
01:13:26,200 --> 01:13:28,300
現在 大家都回到體育館
Right now, all of you get back to the gym.

1164
01:13:28,800 --> 01:13:30,200
都動起來!
Everyone move!

1165
01:13:30,400 --> 01:13:33,700
都不許動! FBl!
Everyone freeze! FBl!

1166
01:13:34,600 --> 01:13:35,800
不許動! ClA!
Stop! ClA!

1167
01:13:37,400 --> 01:13:38,700
計量局!
Bureau of Weights and Measures!

1168
01:13:40,700 --> 01:13:43,500
以後 你得先出來
ln the future, you should probably go first.

1169
01:13:55,200 --> 01:13:57,300
維吉爾 這正是我要說的 來吧
Virgil, that's what l was talking about. Come on.

1170
01:14:17,100 --> 01:14:18,800
我們得趕快把所有人撤離!
We need to get these people out of here now!

1171
01:14:26,000 --> 01:14:29,800
那我們得進黑洞 關閉它?
So, we're supposed to go inside the black hole and close it?

1172
01:14:29,900 --> 01:14:31,800
據我所知 這是唯一的出路
As far as l can figure, it's the only way.

1173
01:14:32,100 --> 01:14:33,530
我們要帶著這個控制器
We'll take the remote pack with us

1174
01:14:33,686 --> 01:14:35,399
改變我們著陸的極性
and reverse the polarity once we land.

1175
01:14:35,400 --> 01:14:37,300
什麼東西?      我一直在研究
What pack?         l've been working on

1176
01:14:37,400 --> 01:14:39,800
一種控制我們從另一邊跳出的新方法
a new way to control our jumps from the other side.

1177
01:14:40,400 --> 01:14:42,000
好吧 帶上電話
OK, hold the phone.

1178
01:14:42,100 --> 01:14:44,600
我們不能讓學生進去 他們會死的
We can't let these students go in that, they could die!

1179
01:14:44,700 --> 01:14:45,826
別無選擇
We have no choice.

1180
01:14:45,994 --> 01:14:48,299
他們是唯一熟悉使用這個儀器的人
They're the only ones familiar with the equipment.

1181
01:14:48,300 --> 01:14:50,500
要是他們不去 我們就得死
lf they don't go then we could all die.

1182
01:14:53,300 --> 01:14:54,500
快點
God speed.

1183
01:14:56,600 --> 01:14:59,000
是我把一切弄的一團糟
l'm the one who messed everything up.

1184
01:14:59,400 --> 01:15:01,400
我進去 查理和齊克跟這個沒關係
l'll go. Charlie and Zeke had nothing to do with it.

1185
01:15:01,500 --> 01:15:04,300
什麼叫沒關係? 是我發明的
What do you mean, nothing to do with it? l invented it.

1186
01:15:04,400 --> 01:15:05,800
我是幫兇      不 你沒有
l helped.          No, you didn't.

1187
01:15:05,900 --> 01:15:08,100
我有過      你刷的油漆!
Yeah, l did.         You painted it!

1188
01:15:09,400 --> 01:15:10,300
打擾一下
Excuse me.

1189
01:15:12,700 --> 01:15:15,300
好吧 夠了 夠了
OK. Enough! Enough!

1190
01:15:16,200 --> 01:15:17,300
你們都去
You'll both go.

1191
01:15:17,800 --> 01:15:21,100
你們也需要我 長官 還有我的鉤子
You'll be needing me too, sir, and my hook.

1192
01:16:02,500 --> 01:16:05,900
聽著 我們一旦轉換了黑洞的極性
Listen, guys, once we've reversed the wormhole's polarity,

1193
01:16:06,000 --> 01:16:08,100
無法計算 多長時間後會關閉
there's no measuring how quickly it will close.

1194
01:16:08,200 --> 01:16:09,774
它可能會開幾分鐘
lt could stay open for several more minutes

1195
01:16:09,904 --> 01:16:12,199
也有可能會瞬間消失
or vanish instantaneously.

1196
01:16:12,200 --> 01:16:13,800
要是我們活著完成任務
And even if we do make it back alive,

1197
01:16:13,900 --> 01:16:14,923
不能保證
there's no guarantee

1198
01:16:15,117 --> 01:16:18,399
我們能回到此刻
we'll return exactly to the point we exited from.

1199
01:16:18,400 --> 01:16:21,300
好的 好的      好運 齊克!
Aye aye, Ser Positive.         Good luck, Zeke!

1200
01:16:25,400 --> 01:16:27,400
維吉爾 聽說你要去拯救世界
Virgil, l hear you're trying to save the world.

1201
01:16:27,500 --> 01:16:30,500
對啊 你哥哥很酷吧?
That's right. Your big brother's pretty cool, huh?

1202
01:16:30,700 --> 01:16:33,700
要是你死了 我可以用你的房間嗎? 我的太小了...
When you die can l have your room? Mine is way too small and...

1203
01:16:33,800 --> 01:16:36,500
