That day that we were tied up together on that stupid Ram statue.

1260
01:21:04,200 --> 01:21:05,200
這天
This day.

1261
01:21:05,700 --> 01:21:09,100
你恨的這天 只是因為讓你有點尷尬
This day you hate so much because you got a little embarrassed?

1262
01:21:10,400 --> 01:21:12,500
