we'll be trapped here for good.

1278
01:22:27,000 --> 01:22:29,500
那維吉爾怎麼辦?      我們不可能去找他
What about Virgil?         There's no way we'll make it to him

1279
01:22:29,600 --> 01:22:31,500
並且準時到達漩渦!
and back to the vortex in time!

1280
01:22:44,100 --> 01:22:45,400
查理! 查理 起來!
Charlie! Charlie, get up!

1281
01:22:45,700 --> 01:22:47,500
起來 查理! 我們得快跑
Get up, Charlie! We gotta keep moving!

1282
01:22:47,900 --> 01:22:48,900
走吧!
Let's go!

1283
