...then l realized, what does he need me for?

1290
01:23:14,500 --> 01:23:16,200
他有一個好朋友在那裡
He's got himself a great friend down there.

1291
01:23:19,000 --> 01:23:20,800
總有一天 他還會有其他的好朋友
And someday he'll have other great friends, too.

