What are you doing?!         What do you mean?

1302
01:24:23,000 --> 01:24:25,600
那是第十四大街 漩渦在後面
That was 1 4th Street! The vortex is back that way.

1303
01:24:25,800 --> 01:24:27,300
我的錯
Oh, my bad.

1304
