我們趕不上了!      沒問題
We're never gonna make it!         No problem.

1305
01:24:46,500 --> 01:24:49,700
鐵鉤!
Whoa!         Yeah, grappling hook!

1306
01:24:49,800 --> 01:24:50,900
擊個掌!
Oh my God!          Yeah!

1307
01:24:51,000 --> 01:24:52,400
手抓住輪子!
Now keep your hand on the wheel!

1308
01:24:57,500 --> 01:24:59,700
衝啊 維吉爾!      快衝啊 不然趕不上了!
Go, Virgil!        Go or we're not gonna make it!

1309
01:25:01,100 --> 01:25:02,600
我們快趕不上了!
We're not gonna make it!

1310
01:25:03,500 --> 01:25:06,700
我們快趕不上了!
We're not gonna make it!

